{
  "2381740": {
    "name": "六方守护者",
    "steam_appid": 2381740,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381740/extras/bacc6aa6045def43b6b832f82ec5d526.avif?t=1728986537\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用随机生成的六边形地块建造您的领地，并控制敌人的入侵路线。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381740/extras/7959c9e1fb2b851623d1455ec0d5da94.poster.avif?t=1728986537\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381740/extras/7959c9e1fb2b851623d1455ec0d5da94.webm?t=1728986537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>击败敌人来获取建造六边形地块的材料。移动和旋转六边形地块来建造更长的道路，获取更佳的建筑摆放位置，甚至关闭传送门来让敌人原地消失！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造防御塔，招募军队，学习法术。击退从陆地、河流和空中进攻的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381740/extras/458c3fce787511c93ab8da480262e981.poster.avif?t=1728986537\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381740/extras/458c3fce787511c93ab8da480262e981.webm?t=1728986537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>选择一种策略来保卫您的领地。建造箭塔和加农炮以及各色法术塔，招募剑士和弓箭手以及骑兵和法师，学习各种强大的法术和咒语，击退从陆地、河流和空中入侵您的领地的各种敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造强大的奇观，扭转乾坤。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381740/extras/4a34a8f2c8d0e9d32348a15fda901beb.poster.avif?t=1728986537\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381740/extras/4a34a8f2c8d0e9d32348a15fda901beb.webm?t=1728986537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>建造有着强大而独特能力的各种奇观，扭转战局。建造风车磨坊，市场等支援建筑来获取额外的金币，购买更强大的火力支持。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充分利用环境要素，左右战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381740/extras/6dfb106bca2f5ed64650d7f16fbc3272.poster.avif?t=1728986537\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381740/extras/6dfb106bca2f5ed64650d7f16fbc3272.webm?t=1728986537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>充分利用地形和环境因素。在高地环境中，您可以将防御塔建造在高地上来扩大它们的打击范围。在沙漠、雪原、雨林中召唤沙尘暴，大雪和大雨来延缓敌人的进攻。巧妙利用元素之间的组合触发强大的元素反应，击溃敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打败难缠的精英敌人，收获祝福。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381740/extras/f26593fe27e3d8cf6c05ea655cfc18cd.poster.avif?t=1728986537\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381740/extras/f26593fe27e3d8cf6c05ea655cfc18cd.webm?t=1728986537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>打败拥有强大独特能力的精英敌人，获得一次选取祝福的机会。这些祝福有的能增强您获取金币的能力，有的能强化您的防御塔和单位，有的能增强您的地形优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坚守尽可能多的天数，来解锁新地图、新建筑、新单位、新法术和新奇观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您每多坚持一天，就可以获得更多的奖杯。消耗奖杯来解锁新地图、新建筑、新单位、新法术和新奇观，以及其他多种多样的天赋能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了传统的轻度肉鸽游戏模式，还有策略性更强的2种构筑模式供您挑战！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语",
